      • scoreNonMandatoryPairs

        public Pair[][] scoreNonMandatoryPairs()
        Assigns a score to every possible non-mandatory Student-Teacher Pair. This method should be run after getMandatoryPairs since getMandatoryPairs will remove from the Students and Teachers ArrayLists the Students and Teachers who are placed into mandatory Pairs.
        Returns:
        Pair[][] representing the Pairs made by matching every Student with every Teacher
